title: 12/19 Fantasy Football Podcast: Waiver Wire (Championship Edition!)
description:
Need a fill-in to win your league this week? We'll give you our priorities at QB (8:00) including Nick Foles and Joe Flacco, RB (14:05) including Bilal Powell and Kerwynn Williams, WR (20:06) including Mike Wallace and Martavis Bryant, TE (22:48) including Eric Ebron and Cameron Brate, DST (25:00), IDP (26:54) and Kicker (28:00) ... Recapping ATL-TB (32:03) and DAL-OAK (36:15) with our thoughts on a disappointing Dak Prescott and much more ... Approve the Move (41:45)! Plus a closer look at the Waiver Wire (44:24) at each position ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
 
To learn more about listener data and our privacy practices visit: https://www.audacyinc.com/privacy-policy
